    {
      "instruction": "<p>Coat the <strong>butterflied chicken</strong> in the <strong>flour</strong>, tap off any excess, then add to the <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and finally press into the <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>firmly to evenly coat all over – this is your <strong>breaded chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1684228315342-x200.jpg",
