            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> (enough to cover the whole base of the pan) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>breaded chicken</strong> and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until golden and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>Indian-style spiced chicken schnitzel</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1684228365186-x200.jpg",
