            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix </strong>with<strong> half</strong> your<strong> mayo</strong>, <strong>half </strong>your<strong> white wine vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>– this is your <strong>slaw</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the<strong> remaining mayo </strong>and <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>with the<strong> chopped garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) – this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1684228372248-x200.jpg",
