            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are golden, remove the tray from the oven and drizzle over your <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and return the tray to the oven for a final 5 min – these are your<strong> spicy potatoes</strong></p>",
