    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Indian-style spiced chicken schnitzel </strong>with the <strong>spicy potatoes</strong>,<strong> slaw </strong>and <strong>garlic mayo </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
